---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy — CloakShare" description="CloakShare privacy policy. How we handle your data." canonical="/privacy">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-mono font-bold text-4xl text-foreground mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-text-tertiary font-mono text-sm mb-12">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans leading-relaxed">
        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-3">Overview</h2>
          <p>
            CloakShare is an open-source document sharing platform. This policy applies to the cloud-hosted
            service at cloakshare.dev. If you self-host CloakShare, your own privacy policy applies.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-3">Data we collect</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Account data</strong> — Email address and hashed password when you register.</li>
            <li><strong>Uploaded files</strong> — Documents and videos you upload for sharing. Files are stored encrypted and deleted when you revoke the link.</li>
            <li><strong>View analytics</strong> — Viewer email (if email-gating is enabled), device type, country, time spent, and pages viewed. This data is shown to you in your dashboard.</li>
            <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — API request counts for billing purposes.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-3">Data we don't collect</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>We don't use third-party analytics or tracking scripts.</li>
            <li>We don't sell or share your data with advertisers.</li>
            <li>We don't read your uploaded documents.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-3">Data retention</h2>
          <p>
            Your files are retained as long as the link is active. When you revoke a link, all rendered
            pages and video segments are permanently deleted from storage. Account data is retained until
            you delete your account.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-3">GDPR</h2>
          <p>
            You can request export or deletion of all your data by contacting us. We process data under
            legitimate interest (providing the service) and consent (account creation). View analytics
            are processed under the legitimate interest of the link creator.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For privacy questions, email <a href="mailto:privacy@cloakshare.dev" class="text-accent hover:underline">privacy@cloakshare.dev</a>
            or open an issue on <a href="https://github.com/cloakshare/cloakshare" class="text-accent hover:underline">GitHub</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
